{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But these were not live ones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But basically, the livelihood was a textile store that we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, you have to understand that textiles there, it wasn't finished clothing and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Each one used to come and buy so many meters for a suit or for a dress or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then that particular person went to his own tailor, and he had it done, tailored for him to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was only in the bigger cities that you saw garments, finished ones, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Otherwise, it was all tailored by local tailors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my mother's business.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was involved in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Father was involved too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember when geese-- the farmers used to bring the geese, and Father used to buy geese.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he used to give them a little kind of receipt, saying-- and he used to send to Mother, to go ahead and be paid.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they used to come to the store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So sometimes they used to spend the money, or they didn't spend the money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother used to give them the money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's how it worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It-- Father didn't carry too much money in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I-- it's-- I was involved, I know, I went twice in summer camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a Betar organization.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a bookkeeper who used to come, an accountant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, in Poland, it wasn't-- yes, it was from the right of center, that-- insofar as Poland was concerned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It-- well, you would call it right because it was Betinski was a leader of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this particular accountant, he suggested for a camp, a summer camp, to be sent to around Seinai, which was closer to the Lithuanian border.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suwalki, Seinai, next to the Lithuanian border.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
